originalText.text: I asked Justin of the Keats Agency how I could lower my auto insurance premiums and right away he sent me a few suggestions for defensive driving courses. He even got me a slight discount on the course! My wife and I took the course, sent him the certificate and again took care of the last step right away. Now we have a discount for 3 years. Great value and great service! I highly recommend them!

originalText.text: I've been consistently impressed with The Keats Agency, I regularly refer clients and this office exceeds expectations every time. Clients have praised their seamless service and prompt claim handling. I wholeheartedly recommend The Keats Agency. Their commitment to excellence, personalized approach, and top-tier customer service make them an outstanding choice in the insurance industry.
